Senior Java Support Lead
Location: Phoenix, AZ
Duration: 9+ month contract


Our South Phoenix client is seeking to hire an experienced Java Application Support Lead for a 9+ month contract. 
Experience must include application production support and development related to web (J2EE) applications. 
 
Day to day responsibilities include analyzing issues encountered by partners, providing analysis of the issues and suggesting solutions. 
Good understanding of design and coding principles. 
The person in the role should be able to go deep into issues as required and isolate root cause of issues and suggest solutions. 
The person in this role should have expertise and passion for analyzing and fixing root cause of problems should be familiar with object oriented design and development. 
The person in this role will work with support tools to prioritize and manage issues. 
Primary areas of responsibility include Software support, development Knowledge of Java and related technologies are desired. 
Innovation, creativity, leadership and the ability to communicate effectively to customers, partners and other engineers is critical for this position.
 
Specific skills: 
Java 1.6 
JSP / HTML / AJAX / Java Script / CSS / Struts 
 
 
If you have any questions please feel free to call me.
 
Thanks & Regards,Arun Chandupatla.
Hallmark Global Technologies Inc. 
262 Chapman Rd, Suite # 101, 
Newark, DE- 19702.
Direct:  302-525-4225
Alt : 302-355-2324/302-525-4228/
